@startuml
title BP-04 - Parent Student Relationship Management

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  DiamondBackgroundColor White
  DiamondBorderColor Black
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
}

|Academic Staff|
start
:Search parent account;
if (Parent account exists?) then (Yes)
  :Select parent account;
else (No)
  :Create parent user account;
  :Assign PARENT role for tenant;
endif

:Search student record;

|Platform|
:Validate parent user belongs to tenant;
:Validate student belongs to tenant;
:Check existing parent student relationship;

if (Relationship already exists?) then (Yes)
  :Return existing relationship;
else (No)
  :Create ParentStudent record;
  :Set relationship type and primary flag;
endif

|Parent Guardian|
:Login to parent workspace;
:View linked children;
stop

note right
Business rules:
- One parent can have many students.
- One student can have many guardians.
- Parent can only view bills for linked students.
end note
@enduml
